	<a href="https://calmatters.org/author/guest-commentary/" class="author">By Guest Commentary <img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/33ab0d2459dbbb6757d4c1275baa8bc8?s=96&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' class='avatar avatar-96 photo' height='96' width='96' /></a>	<span class="published">published: <time datetime="2020-04-17T05:30:35-07:00">April 17, 2020</time></span>
