				<h2 class="largeheadline ">Don’t ban biking during the coronavirus pandemic</h2>
				<div class="featured-image">
	<div class="image">
		<img width="861" height="529" src="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/cycling.jpg?fit=861%2C529" class="attachment-large-wide-rec size-large-wide-rec wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/cycling.jpg?w=2208 2208w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/cycling.jpg?w=300 300w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/cycling.jpg?w=768 768w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/cycling.jpg?w=1024 1024w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/cycling.jpg?w=1536 1536w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/cycling.jpg?w=2048 2048w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/cycling.jpg?w=460 460w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/cycling.jpg?w=348 348w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/cycling.jpg?w=780 780w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/cycling.jpg?w=860 860w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/cycling.jpg?w=861 861w" sizes="(max-width: 861px) 100vw, 861px" />	</div>
	<div class="imagebyline">
					<svg role="img" class="icon icon--camera" aria-label="camera"><use xlink:href="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/themes/thenewsproject/dist/svg/dist/symbol/svg/sprite.symbol.svg#camera"></use></svg>			<span>Photo via iStock</span>
